      "rationale": "Only the Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model is used. No comparison against alternative model forms (Bludszuweit, Arora) has been conducted. Model form uncertainty is a dominant unquantified source of error at MRL 5. Achieved level 2 against required level 5."
